<subSubSection id="15DE5FE0FF83EF40FF42F973FDFBF8C8" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF83EF40FF42F973FB7BF8F4" blockId="43.[151,1436,1661,1905]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FF42F973FEE7F958" bold="true" box="[199,338,1734,1760]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Comments:</emphasis>
This species, as other within 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FD1FF973FCB0F958" box="[666,773,1734,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" genus="Scaphura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FD1FF973FCB0F958" box="[666,773,1734,1760]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Scaphura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, presents mimetic polymorphism that represents a Batesian mimic of wasps (
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FEDBF95FFE51F8BC" box="[350,484,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Pompilidae</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FE74F95EFCB0F8BC" authority="Dahlbom, 1843" authorityName="Dahlbom" authorityYear="1843" box="[497,773,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" genus="Entypus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FE74F95EFDFEF8BC" box="[497,587,1771,1796]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Entypus</emphasis>
Dahlbom, 1843
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FCC4F95EFBF2F8BC" authority="Fabricius, 1804" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1804" box="[833,1095,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" genus="Pepsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FCC4F95EFC3FF8BC" box="[833,906,1771,1796]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Pepsis</emphasis>
Fabricius, 1804
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FBD0F95FFB0AF8BC" box="[1109,1215,1770,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Vespidae</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FB4EF95FFF66F890" authority="Ashmead, 1904" authorityName="Ashmead" authorityYear="1904" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Polistes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FB4EF95FFA91F8BC" box="[1227,1316,1770,1796]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Polistes</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="3955719AFF83EF40FAAEF95FFF66F890" author="Ashmead, W. H." pageId="43" pageNumber="44" pagination="127 - 158" refId="ref28867" refString="Ashmead, W. H. (1904) Descriptions of new genera and species of Hymenoptera from the Philippine Islands. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 28 (1387), 127 - 158. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.28 - 1387.127" type="journal article" year="1904">Ashmead, 1904</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
), serving as a model to behavioural and evolutionary ecology studies (
<bibRefCitation id="3955719AFF83EF40FB81F8BBFB0EF890" author="Del-Claro, K." box="[1028,1211,1806,1832]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" refId="ref31638" refString="Del-Claro, K. (1991) Polimorfismo mimetico de Scaphura nigra Thunberg, 1824 (Tettigoniidae: Phaneropterinae). Dissertacao de Mestrado, Programa de Pos-graduacao em Ecologia. Universidade Estadual de Campinas, Sao Paulo, 75 pp." type="book" year="1991">Del-Claro 1991</bibRefCitation>
). We only recorded specimens similar to the 
<taxonomicName id="9AC477E8FF83EF40FE2BF886FE42F8F4" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1804" box="[430,503,1843,1868]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" genus="Pepsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF83EF40FE2BF886FE42F8F4" box="[430,503,1843,1868]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Pepsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
pattern (
<bibRefCitation id="3955719AFF83EF40FDDFF887FCB8F8F4" author="Del-Claro, K." box="[602,781,1842,1868]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" refId="ref31638" refString="Del-Claro, K. (1991) Polimorfismo mimetico de Scaphura nigra Thunberg, 1824 (Tettigoniidae: Phaneropterinae). Dissertacao de Mestrado, Programa de Pos-graduacao em Ecologia. Universidade Estadual de Campinas, Sao Paulo, 75 pp." type="book" year="1991">Del-Claro 1991</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="3955719AFF83EF40FC9CF887FB74F8F4" author="Del-Claro, K. &amp; Vasconcellos-Neto, J." box="[793,1217,1842,1868]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" pagination="288 - 308" refId="ref31680" refString="Del-Claro, K. &amp; Vasconcellos-Neto, J. (1992) Os padroes de coloracao animal: exemplos na Serra do Japi. In: Morellato, L. C. P. Historia Natural da Serra do Japi: ecologia e preservacao de uma area florestal no Sudeste do Brasil. Editora da UNI- CAMP / FAPESP, Campinas, pp. 288 - 308." type="book chapter" year="1992">Del-Claro &amp; Vasconcellos-Neto 1992</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF83EF40FF42F8E3FDFBF8C8" blockId="43.[151,1436,1661,1905]" box="[199,590,1878,1905]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">
